My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 12

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

It's the final instant restaurant of group two with designer Jess and miner Felix presenting their menu. Will these friends strike gold in the kitchen? Plus, the teams meet the gate crashers.
